npm run dev - will start dev environment with nodemon
nodemon allows to restart the server when changes are made


npm i express-async-handler
we are going to use mongo so we need to write async before every route - contactController
Also we need to handle error using try catch
but to avoid defining try catch in each and every function, we make use of express-async-handler


